Feels good to be back in the gym! I used to spend many hours in the gym, working on strength, mobility and fitness. But ever since the car accident I struggled getting back into a routine, I noticed lately that Im scared of pushing myself out of my comfort zone. When you deal with headaches and neck pain on a weekly base it gets to you 🤯🥴. Im stoked I crossed paths with @addison.bain from @lab.one.two Someone that understand my injury, is able to guide me and pushes me only when my body and head are letting me. Looking forward to keep it going and keep sharing this journey with all of you! 🏋🏻‍♂️ #gym #tbi #mtbtraining #crankitupmtb

My $155 dollar Sprinter Van bed system! It takes me about 4min to lower my bed, or put it back up! The main reason for me getting a van was so I can have my bikes inside, and without having to take my front wheel off! I also wanted the possibility of putting the bed back up, out of the way for when not camping and using the van on a daily base for coaching. Stoked on how it turned out! #vanlife #sprinter #diy #camping #vanbuild 

- I used 3x Ikea midbeam support. $15

Do a modified work out, get out of the house, get out of a funky headspace and move the body. 9 out of the 10 times I’ll feel better after. 🤘 #gym #mentalhealth #tbi

I will follow up on this subject soon, and will go more into details on this! #mtb #skills #crankitupmtb

In our newest trail video with @annekebeerten, we bring Anneke to visit @colermountainbikepreserve and show everything they have to offer and take you down Family Flow. This green trail is accessible for all levels of riders whether you’re riding smoothly on the ground, getting air over the rollers, or absolutely sending it across the bridge. It’s also wide enough for adaptive riders! You’ll find over 22 miles of trails at Coler with cross country, technical, and downhill/enduro options, so there truly is something for everyone to pick. Be sure to take a quick break from riding and enjoy Airship at the Homestead, located in the middle of the preserve. Hope to see you soon and #CatchYouAtColer!

📽️ Video produced by @ndersonta / @bentondrones

WIN THIS BIKE! 🔥 In collab with @iamspecialized_mtb we are GIVING AWAY this brand new P3 DIRTJUMPER!! Come out to the @bombsquad_senders_union Summer Series this Thursday at the @the_railyard in Rogers. 

Here is how you can win this bike:
All lines and sections of the Railyard will be open to session. We will have multiple secret judges out on course all night. Each judge will select 2 or 3 people as standout riders from the evening. All rider names will go into a hat and at the end of the session we will randomly select the winner of the bike!!! 

We will be selecting riders based off of:
-Best Style
-Best Tricks
-Best Youth Rider Under 16
-Most Stoked Rider
-Most Laps

🤘 Some clips from my week of intensive TBI training @thefunctionalneurologycenter Working on a longer video for youtube were I will go into more details! Im motivated to keep sharing this journey with you all, bring more awareness to concussions and tbi injuries!
